==English==
===Etymology===
From '''Xerox'''&#8482;, the trademark name for a type of [[photocopier]], via ''[[xerography]]'' from Greek ''[[xero]]'' meaning dry and ''[[graphy]]'' meaning writing

===Noun===
'''xerox'''
# A Xerox brand [[photocopier]].
#: ''Our new photocopying machine is a Xerox.''

